---
title: Honey-Glazed Beef Rissoles & Tomato Salsa with Couscous Salad & Yoghurt
description: Fly away to the clouds with this fluffy bowl of couscous with plump beef rissoles. Float on a flavourful honey drizzle that coats
the rissoles and will send your tastebuds to dreamland, especially when you add a tomato salsa to the mix.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/honey-glazed-beef-koftas-tomato-salsa-386f3bd0.jpg
